In this evaluation mode, stage-1 recall by {\em def} and {\em amp} increases by ca. 10 points, reaching 93% and 92%, respectively. 
This is intuitive, as pooled ground truth is a subset of the fully hand-crafted ground truth.
The numerical gains carry over to Stage 2: with {\em thr80}, {\em amp} goes up to 56.5% R@P50 and 41.4% R@P80.